reviewText:
+fun game with nice online/offline gameplay (more players = more/stronger enemies);
+goes very well on my low-low-low-end pc with no lag... ever;
+i paid just US$1 on this game+Zeno Clash+Zeno Clash 2+Dwarfs?! (Humble Bundle), which i can say was very worthful.

-this game should have at least a tutorial (i spent a whole day making my girlfriend memorize the controls and how to kill each enemy);
-the achievements: SERIOUSLY? 252 achvs?
